        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Canva's AI features include: Magic Design (generate complete designs from prompts), Magic Eraser (remove unwanted objects from images), AI image generation (text-to-image), Magic Write (AI copywriting inside designs), background removal, and Brand Kit for consistent branding across all assets."
